<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 03:14:49 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>据英国《金融时报》报道，中国恒大清算人对普华永道提起法律诉讼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-evergrandes-liquidators-initiate-legal-action-against-pwc-ft-reports-2024-08-07/</link><description>据英国《金融时报》周二报道，陷入困境的房地产巨头中国恒大集团的清算人已对普华永道采取法律行动，指责其在为集团工作时“疏忽”和“失实陈述”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 02:46:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-evergrandes-liquidators-initiate-legal-action-against-pwc-ft-reports-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>日本央行官员表示如果市场波动则不会加息，日元下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-yen-wobbles-traders-consider-rate-cut-bets-carry-2024-08-07/</link><description>日本央行副行长内田信一表示，在金融市场不稳定时央行不会加息，周三美元走强，兑日元汇率飙升2%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 01:52:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-yen-wobbles-traders-consider-rate-cut-bets-carry-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>日本央行放弃加息后亚洲股市延续涨势，日元回落</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-07/</link><description>周三亚洲股市在日经指数反弹的带动下延续涨势，此前日本央行出人意料地表示在市场波动之际不愿进一步加息，导致日元大幅下跌。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 01:45:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>Shabab Al-Ahli 在亚洲冠军联赛精英赛中发起了 Al-Gharafa 冲突</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/shabab-al-ahli-set-up-al-gharafa-clash-asian-champions-league-elite-2024-08-07/</link><description>阿拉伯联合酋长国的沙巴布·阿赫利在伊斯法罕加时赛中以 4-1 的比分战胜伊朗东道主塞帕汉，下周将迎战卡塔尔的阿尔加拉法，争夺新一届亚洲冠军联赛精英赛的小组赛席位。周二。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 00:55:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/shabab-al-ahli-set-up-al-gharafa-clash-asian-champions-league-elite-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：“周二周转”暂时缓解紧张情绪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-06/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 21:48:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国需求改善，Vans 母公司 VF Corp 第一季度营收降幅小于预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/vans-parent-vf-corp-posts-smaller-q1-revenue-drop-than-expected-better-china-2024-08-06/</link><description>VF Corp 周二公布，由于中国业务改善以及库存水平下降，第一季度营收降幅小于预期，导致其股价在盘后交易中上涨约 7%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 21:42:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/vans-parent-vf-corp-posts-smaller-q1-revenue-drop-than-expected-better-china-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国学者在美充当外国代理人被判刑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/chinese-academic-convicted-acting-foreign-agent-us-2024-08-06/</link><description>周二，一名中国学者被判在美国非法充当外国代理人，他收集了纽约支持中国民主的活动人士的信息，并与北京分享了他的调查结果。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 17:13:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/chinese-academic-convicted-acting-foreign-agent-us-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>彭博社称，巴基斯坦已获得主要贷方一年期债务展期的承诺</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-has-one-year-debt-rollover-commitments-key-lenders-bloomberg-says-2024-08-06/</link><description>据彭博社周二报道，巴基斯坦已获得中国、沙特阿拉伯和阿联酋的承诺，将债务展期一年，这对等待国际货币基金组织最终批准一项新的 70 亿美元贷款计划的卡拉奇来说是一个提振。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 16:09:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-has-one-year-debt-rollover-commitments-key-lenders-bloomberg-says-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>美澳会谈重点关注中国的“胁迫行为”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/australia-highlights-growing-us-military-presence-ahead-ausmin-talks-2024-08-06/</link><description>官员称，美国和澳大利亚周二启动了高层会谈，重点讨论中国的“胁迫行为”、AUKUS核潜艇项目和中东日益紧张的局势。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 14:52:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/australia-highlights-growing-us-military-presence-ahead-ausmin-talks-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>梅洛尼总理访华后意大利与中国签署协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/deals-signed-by-italy-china-after-pm-melonis-trip-2024-08-06/</link><description>意大利总理梅洛尼7月底访问中国，以加强与世界第二大经济体的合作，并在退出“一带一路”基础设施投资计划后重置贸易关系。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 14:51:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/deals-signed-by-italy-china-after-pm-melonis-trip-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>跳水——中国选手全勇夺得女子10米跳台金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/diving-chinas-quan-wins-gold-womens-10m-platform-2024-08-06/</link><description>中国选手权红婵周二在女子10米跳台比赛中夺冠，为中国在巴黎奥运会上夺得第五枚跳水金牌。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 14:39:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/diving-chinas-quan-wins-gold-womens-10m-platform-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>排球-土耳其击败中国队首次进入半决赛，美国和巴西晋级</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/volleyball-turkey-edge-china-reach-first-semi-final-brazil-also-through-2024-08-06/</link><description>周二，欧洲冠军土耳其队在一场拉锯战中以3-2击败中国队，首次进入奥运会女排半决赛，而美国队则直落两盘击败波兰队晋级。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 13:48:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/volleyball-turkey-edge-china-reach-first-semi-final-brazil-also-through-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>市场监管机构称特斯拉将在中国修理170万辆汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-fix-17-mln-vehicles-china-says-market-regulator-2024-08-06/</link><description>国家市场监管机构周二表示，特斯拉正在通过无线软件更新对中国 170 万辆汽车进行远程召回。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 13:15:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-fix-17-mln-vehicles-china-says-market-regulator-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>白宫称中国将加强对芬太尼化学品的监管</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-beef-up-regulations-fentanyl-chemicals-white-house-says-2024-08-06/</link><description>白宫周二表示，中国表示将开始对三种用于制造非法芬太尼的化学品的生产加强控制和监管，称此举“向前迈出了宝贵的一步”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 12:34:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-beef-up-regulations-fentanyl-chemicals-white-house-says-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>意大利的梅洛尼表示，她带女儿去中国为母亲们树立了榜样</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/italys-meloni-says-she-set-example-mothers-by-taking-daughter-china-2024-08-06/</link><description>意大利总理梅洛尼表示，带七岁女儿对中国进行正式访问树立了良好榜样，有助于促进职业母亲的权利。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 12:30:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/italys-meloni-says-she-set-example-mothers-by-taking-daughter-china-2024-08-06/</guid></item></channel></rss>